{"tid":1367574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法緩組朋友：有啲嘢想同班熱血後生講，特別唔好覺得接濟係老奉","createTime":"2019-07-26T09:57:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T17:11:11.000Z","uid":272444,"like":339,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"14898f1bb48ce0aa1c56e1a9ac75c6f3fa67bc65","tid":1367574,"uid":272444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:57:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">以下係代法緩組朋友出po <br />\n只幫佢改過少少字眼</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">TLDR</span>: 請各位對自己、對人地都要量力而為</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n我都明白年輕人有股熱血，係真係想做到啲野、去比啲顏色呢個垃圾政權睇。<br />\n場運動搞咗咁耐，個政權都仲係死不悔改，藍絲同某啲建制議員嘅嘴臉真係好撚噁心，到而家甚至出埋黑社會，<span style=\"color: orange;\">大家覺得受打擊、不忿、好想做啲嘢係好正常。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但亦都希望你地明白，每個人都<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各有難處</span></strong>，亦唔係每個人每次都可以出到嚟。<br />\n出到嚟做野，大人嘅社會同學生真係完全唔同，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">亦唔好講咩「有心出一定出到」⋯⋯</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似當年雨傘嘅時候我仲讀緊書，冇乜包伏會夠薑唔單止走堂、甚至send email比lecturer同佢講我要去瞓馬路所以我唔返學啦，<span style=\"color: orange;\">但而家返工出到嚟社會好多嘢真心身不由己。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我公司有後生仔響應不合作活動著黑衫戴口罩，都要比班廢老指指點點，人地話咁啱病咗都唔聽，死都夾人係黃絲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">參與到係好事，但嚟唔到都一定有佢嘅考慮。</span></strong></span><br />\n勇武自然係值得尊敬，但係成場運動唔會淨係需要勇武，請大家記住有一班勇唔到嘅後援幫緊你地，文宣、法援、物資，<strong>大家各有各做，係唔同嘅方面出力就得，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請唔好怪人點解唔乜乜乜。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外我真係<strong>千萬千萬拜託各位手足</strong>，特別係<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">未成年</span></strong>個啲：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你地可以衝，但唔好熱血上頭唔諗後果。</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我已經接觸過幾位<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">十幾歲</span></strong>嘅手足，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>冇錢又冇地方住</strong></span>，又因為同家人政見問題<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔返屋企</strong></span>，日日係街度參與唔同地方嘅活動。<br />\n我唔係話你地參加有問題，我好多謝你地肯出力添。<br />\n但參加完之後<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">次次要搵人接濟你地</span></span></strong>，比地方你地住/請你地食飯（<strong>有啲仲老奉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>），其實都係一種<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不必要嘅消耗</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尤其唔係個個人都可以財大氣粗咁講句「<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">我養你！</span></strong>」咁架嘛，有好多人屋企都唔方便收留大家，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可以收留嘅數其實好有限。</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔少搞到接濟你嘅手足屋企人對參加呢場運動更加反感（Sor係呀又係失民心論） ，有啲仲試過<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">報埋警</span></span></strong>，搞親人地又令自己冒險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我甚至聽過有人話想<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">做黑工搵錢</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係拜託你地，幾唔甘心都好，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>量力而為啦乖啦</strong></span>，何必搵自己較飛呢⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己屋企都係藍，好明白各位真係好難受，但冇能力獨立之前希望大家忍一忍，你有咩事大家一定會幫你，但呢場係長期戰嚟，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>盡己所能爬山就得。</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">法緩組都會攰，希望大家互相支撐，唔好勉強自己又勉強人地。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1ad472c325e6df28ca657684cb6281d67f456142","tid":1367574,"uid":272444,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:01:46.000Z","msg":"我的朋友不是我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫你唔係問題，但依加個情況已經去到濫用人地好心，甚至有人話要佢請飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見住佢又要救人又要周圍搵人接濟啲冇錢又唔生性嘅細路，頭都大埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc30c447ec559324ceecf69eac53b685f53499ff","tid":1367574,"uid":272444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:07:31.000Z","msg":"推，希望多啲後生睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9173dd75bc755316015d405ff17cef5800dd8005","tid":1367574,"uid":272444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62be44c639a3276f4abd9eacd1991661a65c3318","tid":1367574,"uid":266132,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:10:22.000Z","msg":"一味熱血唔係大哂....大家最低限度要照顧到自己呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> pish"},{"pid":"c8b170c557740b47e5576b92e8461ea9c8311351","tid":1367574,"uid":272444,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c92f273dbdf27baa7c8971bea29e3a79da600a","tid":1367574,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:12:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f60da1ddf9d7ac3c04a2621054c8998fa652c5c0","tid":1367574,"uid":138060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a73c06fe0b23b02a24624045d19a5a3c19ee312","tid":1367574,"uid":272444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:14:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4376a660653c660c48f7b29af7a21a2cc3864b50","tid":1367574,"uid":272444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d732009a662c09ad362cf833f8e99823b0c3841b","tid":1367574,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:17:09.000Z","msg":"加油 我地都係香港人"},{"pid":"3eeaa29011a820e5bea930a4970643619b2a6d2b","tid":1367574,"uid":272444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea3aafbcc94c3652d1139479a3f04b69a33d0792","tid":1367574,"uid":149702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:27:46.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e0a980559c5da503482a9e8e7b6a617a7c249978","tid":1367574,"uid":272444,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:32:13.000Z","msg":"其實我都覺得好心up，連啲咁細嘅細路都想行出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔好意思都要講句，成場運動嘅資源係有限的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再推，希望多啲人睇到，你唔洗認同但我地希望你得個知字都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d393203333c0747b6abc3f7592d8f911d8e2c1f","tid":1367574,"uid":272444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e69be8e6835b9b9fe469b05f3149d08beca8c8a","tid":1367574,"uid":257184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:44:45.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"953792413c7c04a04fe3be2b5858f6365f319a89","tid":1367574,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:46:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dafdaf9b8ff9dd5e44823dc5633940d48b427e45","tid":1367574,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:48:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d5298e5bbea4328718a4726f79421bc22edabe55","tid":1367574,"uid":289551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:49:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26607479c388acfff28918b8ecc1aecc735cd144","tid":1367574,"uid":249885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1ad472c325e6df28ca657684cb6281d67f456142","tid":1367574,"uid":272444,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:01:46.000Z","msg":"我的朋友不是我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫你唔係問題，但依加個情況已經去到濫用人地好心，甚至有人話要佢請飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見住佢又要救人又要周圍搵人接濟啲冇錢又唔生性嘅細路，頭都大埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:50:12.000Z","msg":"咩請飲酒"},{"pid":"b982b8847acc6065e6ff6fc3e7f26fc2e8669eff","tid":1367574,"uid":37220,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:51:02.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n負責任既勇武"},{"pid":"2e256c5ae5922e5ce87c5eced5cfa0af026f3bc3","tid":1367574,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41ed5da92f651fd8ec451ce5b91685fa6c2ab61","tid":1367574,"uid":270352,"like":0,"dislike":30,"score":-30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:54:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8366ed64802e6888199ff28887a284335cb7c0a","tid":1367574,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:56:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c0303e4035e6a480f52a23be907b8edc6cc665","tid":1367574,"uid":270918,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:17:09.000Z","msg":"屋企都有藍，我都認同好辛苦，滿口歪理，其實唔需要同佢地硬踫，因為佢地呢d人寧願聽外人講都唔會聽自己講，所以不如慳返啖氣，自己轉移視線啦。<br />\n我萬分感謝年輕人嘅付出，至少因為你地，令我唔再逃避政治，但原來越暸解越可怕。<br />\n但同樣真係擔心你地，我知道今時今日唔可以用自己嘅睇法apply落你地度，只能希望你們照顧好自己，一定要平安回家。<br />\n各自爬山 一個都不能少"},{"pid":"29b18d46e074685e58142b5ff1462c33d118f77c","tid":1367574,"uid":272569,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:56:00.000Z","msg":"各位後生<br />\n要努力，讀書又好點到好<br />\n將來先更多機會上去做決策者話得事嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做漆黑中嘅螢火蟲 先更容易改變社會"},{"pid":"11928c7691046886269856a7c6fc8328f92ad319","tid":1367574,"uid":262527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:57:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8aede4f9927e86ea3c9269be0e812bb314dabe03","tid":1367574,"uid":182088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:59:22.000Z","msg":"好有道理，要照顧到自己先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010c274df4825a32e0e578e5a79d997b865b2094","tid":1367574,"uid":245523,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:01:10.000Z","msg":"推 幫你真係唔係應份 同埋唔好熱血上頭做岀啲挽回唔到嘅事 你坐監香港人唔會幫你養家 你睇下魚蛋除咗天琦之外啲人仲記得邊個<br />\n要熱血 要勇武 要和理非 亦都要識自己執生"},{"pid":"67795ad4b48bba4fbc461e8cbbca2676fdac499f","tid":1367574,"uid":86090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac89bcc61d6ff3b08c374bd73377b05df4e42a8","tid":1367574,"uid":160176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:11:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"869bc57ad0a8573a713e3ca168fa9407f5bb6f49","tid":1367574,"uid":272444,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"26607479c388acfff28918b8ecc1aecc735cd144","tid":1367574,"uid":249885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1ad472c325e6df28ca657684cb6281d67f456142","tid":1367574,"uid":272444,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:01:46.000Z","msg":"我的朋友不是我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫你唔係問題，但依加個情況已經去到濫用人地好心，甚至有人話要佢請飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見住佢又要救人又要周圍搵人接濟啲冇錢又唔生性嘅細路，頭都大埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:50:12.000Z",